      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just getting harder every day... i feel like i'm always asking for something. a glass of water, help with my meds, someone to help me move a bit. my kids are so busy with their own lives and i can just see it in their eyes when they come over... they're so tired. i hate being such a nuisance to them.",
